}}</ref>{{primary source inline|date=December 2023}} In March 2015, Toyota became a sponsor partner for the [[Olympic Games]], in the form of supplying vehicles and communications between vehicles until 2024.<ref>{{Cite press release |title=IOC Announces Toyota as TOP Partner to 2024 |date=March 13, 2015 |url=https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-announces-toyota-as-top-partner-to-2024 |access-date=January 7, 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107100238/https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-announces-toyota-as-top-partner-to-2024 |archive-date=January 7, 2017 |work=Olympic News}}</ref>{{primary source inline|date=December 2023}}

